NAME: NOTIFICATION_ADMIN
DESCRIPTION: Notification Admin has the ability to perform any admin action related to notifications

NAME: NOTIFICATION_RULE_ADMIN
DESCRIPTION: Notification Rule Admin has the ability to create notification rules

NAME: NOTIFICATION_RULE_TEMPLATE_ADMIN
DESCRIPTION: Notification Rule Template Admin has the ability to create notification rule templates

NAME: NOTIFICATION_RULE_USER
DESCRIPTION: Notification Rule User has the ability to subscribe/unsubscribe etc to notification rules
